thread.title_full: Sheenco Travel reviewed by Katherine Bailey

author: Katherine Bailey
title: Katherine Bailey
text:
We had the best vacation ever!!! Shamrock Travel was great. I had a few, lol, questions and everyone there were so helpful.
We are planning to go to England and Wales in two years and I would like very much for your company to help us with the trip if you do England ans Wales.
Kathy Bailey
